屋企又開始頹返<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:52:28.000Z","msg":"我以前老豆過生果陣都係咁  仲要星期一返學統測<br />\n果陣一路做份卷一路想喊  成份卷都冇心機做  好低分<br />\n同學同老師都知道咩事   但我唔想人擔心  返到學校扮冇野扮開朗<br />\n到左小息果陣忍唔住了  喊到傻  D同學走黎安慰我<br />\n但唔知點解我喊得仲勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果陣每日返到屋企  老母就喊得好勁  我唔想自己都喊埋一份要佢擔心<br />\n所以壓抑左好耐   只係敢偷偷地係床上面喊但又唔喊出聲<br />\n而家就算係老豆死忌都會唸起以前既野<br />\n最慘係有D無腦既FD拎你老豆黎講笑   鬧又唔係唔鬧又唔係<br />\n聽到D FD無啦啦話屌你老豆    我真係好撚想屌柒佢全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我果陣係唸   到底老豆想我做一個點樣既人<br />\n應該唔會想我因為佢搞到自己唔開心<br />\n之後隨住時間先慢慢走出來<br />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3e676ee001faaf8f1d69027888c24bd5b256a5","tid":581732,"uid":151013,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"52f9a6ad53acd8b74f6d945504444b46c8ef423c","tid":581732,"uid":174084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcef0db5bf3bed5a23a3c70423888923df60c3c4","tid":581732,"uid":151013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:47:42.000Z","msg":"由入院到過身都差唔多半年<br />\n<br />\n由個時開始個心一直好煩  好頹廢 做咩都提唔起勁<br />\n<br />\n同朋友出街嘻嘻哈哈完  輕鬆返少少<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企又開始頹返<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:48:18.000Z","msg":"How old is he/she?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:53:49.000Z","msg":"7字頭    <br />\n<br />\n好方面諗<br />\n<br />\n佢唔係即刻走  <br />\n<br />\n有